3. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper discusses the use of molecular communication for monitoring in confined environments, which can be relevant in multi-agent systems. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of a molecular communication system for monitoring and control in confined environments, which is relevant to systems and control. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the use of a molecular communication system for monitoring in confined environments, which can be relevant in robotics applications.
